data.title: Viola Magdalena Fransen Toth (1919
data.meta_description: Hobe Sound, Fl. --   Viola M. Toth, 85, died March 24, 2005.   She was born in Motala, Sweden, and moved to Miami in 1955, then to Hobe Sound in 1970.   She was a member of St. Christopher Catholic Church, Hobe Sound and the Veterans of Foreign Wars.   Before retiring, she was a cashier with the Martin County School...
